# Support Ticket System — Cursor Rules

## Stack
- Next.js 16 + Fastify 5 + PostgreSQL + Drizzle ORM
- pnpm monorepo with packages/shared for Zod schemas

## Patterns
- State machine in packages/shared — never duplicate transition logic
- Status changes ONLY via PATCH /tickets/:id/status
- JWT access + Postgres session for auth
- RBAC at API middleware level

## Quality
- TypeScript strict, ESM modules
- No secrets in repo
- Validate all inputs with Zod from @repo/shared
- Minimal scope changes — match existing conventions

## Testing
- State machine integration tests are mandatory
- Run pnpm test before claiming completion
